title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - FlyByWire A380x - Christmas present
description:
In this video we are going to unpack the early Christmas present from FlyByWire. They have release a special airport which is used the develop the A380x. In this video we will look how you can get this Christmas present and of course have a look at the A380x which is still under development.

If you would like to give the addon a try yourself visit the site below to download it:
https://flybywiresim.com/
